            "title": "財經｜中遠海運國際(00517)去年多賺8.7% 連特別息派29仙",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜中遠海運國際(00517)去年多賺8.7% 連特別息派29仙\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜中遠海運國際(00517)去年多賺8.7% 連特別息派29仙</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中遠海運國際(00517)公布，截至去年底止年度業績，股東應佔盈利7.71億元，按年升8.72%；每股盈利52.6仙。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司派發末期息19仙及特別息10仙，合共29仙。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">期內，收入收入37.06億元，按年升2.17%，主要由於塗料及船舶貿易代理的分 部收入上升所致。</p></div>",
